            "text": "Matthew 2:23",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "; and Jether, though an Israelite, as Aben Ezra observes, is called an Ishmaelite, perhaps because he dwelt some time among that people, ",
            "children": []
